title: Biden Does The Unthinkable (Ep 1589)
description:
A shocking new memo leaks proving that the Biden administration knew Afghanistan would collapse. I also show a video of the California Governor getting destroyed in an interview. 

News Picks:


They knew! Leaked State Department cable indicated that the Biden administration was warned about the collapse of Afghanistan.

The Taliban is in possession of sophisticated US weaponry.


Biden thinks you’ll lose interest in the Afghanistan disaster. 


This is the ultimate humiliation. The Biden Administration is asking for payments to evacuate our people out of Kabul. 


A stunning new report about the Democrats’ efforts to mess with the 2020 election.
